parameters:
(It won't open... It seems like there's someone
inside, though.)

"Is anyone there? Can you hear me? I've come to
help. Can you move right now?"\n<Yukine>
(Huh? No response. I wonder what's wrong.)

"Hey, can you hear me? You're there, aren't you?
Can you hear me?"\n<Yukine>

(There's still no response. I can hear
breathing... so it seems like they're alive. Maybe
they can't speak right now.)
"I'll rescue you soon, so just wait for me."\n<Yukine>
"Just wait a little, I'll help you out soon."\n<Yukine>
(First, I need to find the key to open this.)

"How terrible... To lock up such a little girl and
tie her up with ropes in this state."\n<Yukine>
(Her complexion is poor, I'm really worried.)
"Hey, are you okay? Can you hear my voice?"\n<Yukine>

"Eh, you... can't you speak? And my voice isn't
reaching you...?"\n<Yukine>
(It seems like she can't see me in her eyes.)

"That's so... She can't see either... And yet, she
was left all alone locked up in a place like
this..."\n<Yukine>
"Don't worry, I'll help you out right away..."\n<Yukine>

(But no matter how much strength I use, the ropes
won't loosen.)

"Just wait a bit, I'll untie the ropes soon, so
just hang in there a little longer."\n<Yukine>

(I need to find some tools to untie this child's
ropes.)
"Wait for me, I'll help you right away."\n<Yukine>

"I need to help quickly... I have to find
something to untie the ropes."\n<Yukine>

"Just wait a little longer, I'll go look for it
right away."\n<Yukine>

"With this many gathered, we should be able to
burn through this rope..."\n<Yukine>

While hoping so, I bring the heated talisman close
to the black rope.
The cursed rope was burned through in no time.
"Hey, can you move? Can you hear my voice?"\n<Yukine>\F[8]

Her eyes are vacant, and it seems she can't hear
my voice.\F[8]
"That's right, the doll that ghost lady gave me!"\n<Yukine>\F[17]
"Hey, can you hear me? Can you see me?"\n<Yukine>\F[5]

Even when I hold her hand, there is no response.
\F[10]\AA[F]\FF[20]
It seems she has lost all sensation. \F[10]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"Hmm, what to do? She must be the one who was
asking for help... I can't just leave her here."\n<Yukine>\F[13]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"It would be good if you could walk... Huh? You
can stand?"\n<Yukine>\F[5]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"So... if we hold hands, you can walk even without
feeling your body. Could it be thanks to the charm
and doll from earlier?"\n<Yukine>\F[5]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"I will never abandon you. Come on, let's hold
hands. It's dark and scary here... Let's go back
to a warm place together."\n<Yukine>\F[3]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"Eh... that girl just now... Wait... she's tied up
here..."\n<Yukine>\F[15]

"Huh? Eh... then... who was the girl that was
walking around the mansion until just now?"\n<Yukine>\F[15]

"I can't be scared... I have to hurry and help
her..."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"Ugh... What is this place? There's a terrible
accumulation of evil spirits. It feels like...
it's been sealed for a long time, with no one
coming or going."\n<Yukine>\F[10]
(I wonder if there's anything useful here...)

(I might be able to unlock the prison with this
key)

(I wonder if there's anything else that might be
useful...)
